135
00:10:16,667 --> 00:10:18,900
[approaching footsteps]

136
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:27,700
- HI, MOM.

137
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:50,833
- SKYE, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

138
00:10:50,867 --> 00:10:53,167
- LOOK.

139
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:56,133
