FOR ANYTHING, BUT...

141
00:11:00,433 --> 00:11:03,067
I DIDN'T KNOW
WHERE ELSE TO GO.

142
00:11:07,267 --> 00:11:10,067
- HE CAME BACK
TO THE ROLLERDOME.

143
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:13,300
HE KILLED MORE PEOPLE.

144
00:11:13,333 --> 00:11:15,233
PEOPLE THAT I KNOW.

145
00:11:15,267 --> 00:11:19,067
- SKYE, Y-YOU SHOULDN'T
HAVE COME HERE.

146
00:11:19,067 --> 00:11:21,433
- WELL, WHAT ELSE
AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?

147
00:11:21,467 --> 00:11:23,667
WHEN IT COMES TO
PARENTAL FIGURES,

148
00:11:23,700 --> 00:11:25,800
I DON'T REALLY HAVE
A LOT OF OPTIONS.

149
00:11:25,833 --> 00:11:28,767
SERIAL KILLER DAD
OR MOM WHO ABANDONED ME.

150
00:11:30,667 --> 00:11:32,700
- SKYE, YOU NEED TO GO BACK,
TALK TO THE POLICE.

151
00:11:32,733 --> 00:11:34,100
THEY CAN HELP YOU.

152
00:11:34,133 --> 00:11:36,567
- I'M NOT GOING BACK THERE.

153
00:11:39,233 --> 00:11:43,567
