WORK OUT PRETTY WELL FOR YOU.

154
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:50,300
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT MY LIFE HAS BEEN LIKE

155
00:11:50,333 --> 00:11:53,167
SINCE YOU WALKED OUT?

156
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:55,467
YOU LEFT ME WITH HIM.

157
00:11:55,500 --> 00:12:00,833
- I DID NOT KNOW...
WHAT HE WAS.

158
00:12:00,867 --> 00:12:02,867
HE LOVED YOU SO MUCH.

159
00:12:02,900 --> 00:12:04,100
- AND YOU DIDN'T?

160
00:12:04,133 --> 00:12:07,333
- NO, IT WAS NOT THAT.
IT WAS--

161
00:12:07,367 --> 00:12:09,733
I WAS PRACTICALLY YOUR AGE
WHEN YOU WERE BORN,

162
00:12:09,767 --> 00:12:11,933
AND I WASN'T
READY TO BE A MOTHER.

163
00:12:11,967 --> 00:12:14,100
AND CHARLIE AND I
WEREN'T EVEN MARRIED,

164
00:12:14,133 --> 00:12:17,267
AND IT JUST REALLY SEEMED LIKE
THE BEST IDEA AT THE TIME.

165
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:19,567
I...

166
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,667
I THOUGHT YOU WOULD BE BETTER
OFF WITHOUT ME.

167
00:12:21,700 --> 00:12:23,533
I-I...

168
00:12:26,933 --> 00:12:29,367
UH, I WAS SCARED,
AND I LEFT.

169
00:12:33,767 --> 00:12:36,233
I DON'T HAVE A BETTER
EXPLANATION THAN THAT.

170
00:12:36,267 --> 00:12:38,500
I WISH I DID.
I'M SORRY.

171
00:12:38,533 --> 00:12:42,067
I'M SO SORRY.

172
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:45,967
- MY WHOLE LIFE, I'VE WANTED TO
TELL YOU THAT I HATE YOU.

173
00:12:50,067 --> 00:12:51,633
I JUST REALLY NEED
YOUR HELP OKAY?

174
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,767
- OF COURSE YOU CAN STAY HERE,

175
00:12:57,800 --> 00:13:00,067
AT LEAST UNTIL
WE FIGURE THINGS OUT.

176
00:13:00,067 --> 00:13:01,500
[door closes]

177
00:13:01,533 --> 00:13:04,800
- HEY, MOM, JUST CAME
BACK FOR MY PHONE.

178
00:13:04,833 --> 00:13:06,400
WHAT'S GOING ON?

179
00:13:06,433 --> 00:13:08,167
[door closes]

180
