TELLING ME THIS?

183
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,400
- I UNDERSTAND THIS IS
VERY CONFUSING FOR YOU--

184
00:13:14,433 --> 00:13:17,433
- I'M NOT CONFUSED,
I'M PISSED!

185
00:13:17,467 --> 00:13:20,067
- I UNDERSTAND--
- MOM, WHEN DID THIS HAPPEN?

186
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:22,400
