AT OUR FRONT DOOR.

187
00:13:22,433 --> 00:13:26,067
[muffled yelling continues]

188
00:13:39,133 --> 00:13:41,433
- EXPLAIN IT, EXPLAIN IT!

189
00:13:41,467 --> 00:13:43,100
I WOULD LOVE TO HEAR IT.

190
00:13:43,133 --> 00:13:46,233
- I NEED YOU TO HEAR ME
IN A QUIET PLACE.

191
00:13:46,267 --> 00:13:48,767
CAN YOU TAKE A MOMENT
AND GET CALM, PLEASE?

192
00:14:35,567 --> 00:14:36,933
- HEY.

193
00:14:36,967 --> 00:14:39,700
YOUR MOM LET ME BORROW SOME--

194
00:14:39,733 --> 00:14:41,067
- YOU MEAN YOUR MOM?

195
00:14:43,567 --> 00:14:45,200
IT'S FINE.

196
00:14:45,233 --> 00:14:47,900
- THIS IS A LITTLE WEIRD,
HUH?

197
00:14:47,933 --> 00:14:50,267
- IT'S A LOTTA WEIRD.

198
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:57,133
- SEE YA.

199
00:15:13,133 --> 00:15:15,833
