WHEN SHE WAS LITTLE.

201
00:15:21,767 --> 00:15:24,600
- I LOOKED JUST LIKE THAT.

202
00:15:26,133 --> 00:15:29,533
I'M SORRY
IF I FREAKED ALEX OUT.

203
00:15:29,567 --> 00:15:33,400
- ALEX IS A LITTLE EMOTIONAL.
SHE GETS UPSET EASILY.

204
00:15:37,933 --> 00:15:41,500
