SOMETHING.

205
00:15:41,533 --> 00:15:44,333
ALEX AND TED DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT YOUR FATHER.

206
00:15:44,367 --> 00:15:46,967
THEY DON'T KNOW ABOUT CHARLIE
ROTTER, SO YOU CAN'T--

207
00:15:47,067 --> 00:15:50,767
- TRUST ME,
I'M NOT GOING TO TELL ANYBODY.

208
