00:18:55,967 --> 00:18:58,067
- DUDE, I THINK
THAT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

245
00:18:58,067 --> 00:18:59,867
- [giggling]

246
00:18:59,900 --> 00:19:01,367
- YEAH, LAUGH IT UP MACAFFEE.

247
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:04,333
