AND MACAFFEE.

252
00:19:16,133 --> 00:19:17,967
- REALLY?
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

253
00:19:18,067 --> 00:19:20,933
'CAUSE I'D SAY IT WAS BETWEEN
YOU AND CHARLIE ROTTER AND SKYE.

254
00:19:20,967 --> 00:19:23,367
- THIS ISN'T ABOUT HER.

255
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:26,867
- BRIGG, YOU'VE GOT TO CRANK
DOWN THE CRAZY

256
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:30,133
LIKE 900%, MAN.

257
00:19:30,167 --> 00:19:32,500
