266
00:19:57,067 --> 00:19:59,333
HAVE YOU?

267
00:20:03,433 --> 00:20:05,233
- NO.

268
00:20:07,300 --> 00:20:09,833
- SORRY ABOUT YOUR FACE.

269
00:20:17,833 --> 00:20:19,567
- DOES THAT HURT?

270
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:22,067
