276
00:20:39,667 --> 00:20:41,633
- IT WAS PRETTY COOL THOUGH,
RIGHT?

277
00:20:41,667 --> 00:20:43,633
- I'M COURTNEY.
- I'M--

278
00:20:43,667 --> 00:20:45,333
- DEREK.
I KNOW.

279
00:20:45,367 --> 00:20:47,400
YOU'RE A JUNIOR.

280
00:20:47,433 --> 00:20:50,867
- YEAH.

281
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:52,967
