- CHEMISTRY.

282
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,400
MM-HMM.

283
00:20:55,833 --> 00:20:58,067
- ARE YOU STALKING ME
OR SOMETHING?

284
00:20:58,100 --> 00:21:00,500
'CAUSE I MEAN,
IT'S TOTALLY COOL IF YOU ARE.

285
00:21:00,533 --> 00:21:02,900
- I'M IN YOUR CHEMISTRY CLASS.

286
00:21:02,933 --> 00:21:06,067
- SERIOUSLY?
- YEAH.

287
00:21:06,067 --> 00:21:08,600
- HOW--HOW--HOW COME
I'VE NEVER NOTICED YOU?

288
00:21:08,633 --> 00:21:11,700
- PROBABLY CAUSE YOU WERE
ALWAYS TALKING TO SKYE.

289
00:21:11,733 --> 00:21:15,367
- SKYE.
SKYE WHO?

290
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:57,367
[loud music thuds]

291
00:21:57,400 --> 00:22:00,333
[Shout Out Out Out Out's
 Forever Indebted plays]

292
00:22:00,367 --> 00:22:06,267
*

293
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:09,633
- * BIG DEBTS,
YA KNOW THEY GOT ME *

294
00:22:09,667 --> 00:22:11,667
* MORE THAN I GOT OUT

295
00:22:11,700 --> 00:22:15,600
* AND EVERY MONTH I THINK
I FINALLY HIT THE BOTTOM *

296
00:22:15,633 --> 00:22:17,567
* BUT THEY KEEP GROWIN'

297
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:19,667
* AND FREAKIN' GROWIN'

298
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:23,267
* AND EVERY MONTH I GET IN
DEEPER WITH MY KNOWIN' *

299
00:22:23,300 --> 00:22:26,267
[music changes]

300
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:31,233
*

301
00:22:31,267 --> 00:22:32,600
