I CAN TELL YOU STUFF.

440
00:30:18,333 --> 00:30:21,333
- WELL, YOU CAN.

441
00:30:23,467 --> 00:30:26,200
AND ARE WE LIKE HAVING
A LITTLE LIFETIME MOMENT HERE?

442
00:30:26,233 --> 00:30:29,067
[both giggling]

443
00:30:33,833 --> 00:30:36,467
- I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

444
00:30:36,500 --> 00:30:38,733
- I'M GOING TO GO INSIDE.
- YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

445
00:30:38,767 --> 00:30:40,633
- NAH, BUT I WANT TO.

446
00:30:44,733 --> 00:30:46,367
- LATER, SKYE.

447
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:49,300
SHE'S SO WEIRD.

448
00:30:49,333 --> 00:30:52,400
FYI, EVERYBODY IS TALKING
ABOUT YOUR PARTY.

449
00:30:52,433 --> 00:30:54,767
JAMS WILL NOT SHUT UP
ABOUT YOU.

450
00:30:54,800 --> 00:30:56,900
- REALLY?

451
00:30:56,933 --> 00:30:58,733
- I'M TELLING YOU ALEX,

452
00:30:58,767 --> 00:31:01,167
THROWING THIS PARTY
IS GOING TO BE HUGE FOR YOU.

453
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:03,367
YOU DO THIS AND ON MONDAY,

454
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:05,700
YOU'RE GOING TO BE A COMPLETELY
DIFFERENT PERSON.

455
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:15,633
- OKAY.
- YES!

456
00:31:15,667 --> 00:31:18,067
YOU WON'T REGRET IT,
PROMISE.

457
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,067
- HEY, SKYE.

458
00:32:44,067 --> 00:32:46,867
I DIDN'T MEAN TO SCARE YOU.
I JUST CAME TO GRAB A DRINK.

459
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:54,700
LISTEN,
I KNOW YOU'RE NEW IN TOWN,

460
00:32:54,733 --> 00:32:56,700
SO I JUST WANTED
TO LET YOU KNOW

461
00:32:56,733 --> 00:33:00,400
YOU'RE TOTALLY INVITED TO ALEX'S
PARTY TOMORROW NIGHT.

462
00:33:00,433 --> 00:33:03,300
- I DIDN'T REALIZE
SHE WAS HAVING THE PARTY.

463
00:33:03,333 --> 00:33:05,700
- YEP, SHE JUST DECIDED.

464
00:33:05,733 --> 00:33:07,767
IT'S GOING TO BE SUPER FUN.

465
00:33:07,800 --> 00:33:10,867
DON'T RUIN IT.

466
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:16,067
- WHATEVER.

467
00:33:17,767 --> 00:33:20,700
- CAN'T WAIT TO GET TO
KNOW YOU BETTER.

468
00:33:34,167 --> 00:33:35,733
WHOA.

