1018
01:14:33,967 --> 01:14:36,467
- CHARLIE, LEAVE HER ALONE!

1019
01:14:36,500 --> 01:14:37,567
- CAROLYN.

1020
01:14:37,600 --> 01:14:41,100
- HE HAS ALEX!

1021
01:14:45,933 --> 01:14:48,567
- LET HER GO.

1022
01:14:48,600 --> 01:14:51,067
