YOUR FAMILY BACK.

1042
01:15:49,867 --> 01:15:51,800
- DADDY!

1043
01:15:51,833 --> 01:15:55,400
NO!

1044
01:15:55,433 --> 01:15:56,833
- JUST ONE LAST THING TO DO,

1045
01:15:56,867 --> 01:15:58,933
AND THEN WE'LL ALL BE
TOGETHER AGAIN.

1046
01:15:58,967 --> 01:16:00,900
- STOP, STOP, STOP, STOP!

1047
01:16:00,933 --> 01:16:05,067
YOU'RE HER FATHER!

1048
01:16:05,067 --> 01:16:06,867
- YOU LIE.

1049
01:16:06,900 --> 01:16:09,233
- I WAS PREGNANT
WHEN I LEFT YOU.

1050
01:16:09,267 --> 01:16:11,633
I SWEAR TO GOD.

1051
01:16:11,667 --> 01:16:12,967
I COULDN'T LET YOU HAVE HER TOO,

1052
01:16:13,067 --> 01:16:18,300
YOU SICK MONSTER.

1053
01:16:18,333 --> 01:16:20,967
- YOU KNEW WHAT HE WAS?

1054
01:16:21,067 --> 01:16:24,233
AND YOU LEFT ME WITH HIM?

1055
01:16:24,267 --> 01:16:27,067
- ALL HE CARED ABOUT WAS YOU.

1056
01:16:27,067 --> 01:16:32,067
AS LONG AS HE HAD YOU,
HE WOULD STAY AWAY FROM ME.

1057
01:16:32,067 --> 01:16:33,367
BUT YOU BROUGHT HIM HERE.

1058
01:16:33,400 --> 01:16:37,633
- NO.

1059
01:16:37,667 --> 01:16:39,833
- I NEVER SHOULD HAVE
LET YOU STAY.

1060
01:16:39,867 --> 01:16:41,633
THIS IS ALL YOUR FAULT!

1061
01:16:41,667 --> 01:16:42,867
- SHUT YOUR MOUTH!

1062
01:16:42,900 --> 01:16:44,067
- I WISH THAT YOU WOULD HAVE
NEVER FOUND US,

1063
01:16:44,100 --> 01:16:45,833
AND I WISH THAT YOU
WERE NEVER BEEN BORN!

1064
01:16:45,867 --> 01:16:49,333
- SHUT YOUR MOUTH!

1065
01:16:49,367 --> 01:16:53,633
- NO!

1066
01:16:53,667 --> 01:16:54,800
NO!

1067
01:16:54,833 --> 01:16:58,500
NO!

1068
01:17:03,767 --> 01:17:06,767
- COME ON, COME ON!

1069
01:17:06,800 --> 01:17:07,800
COME ON.
COME ON!

1070
01:17:07,833 --> 01:17:10,300
COME ON!

1071
01:17:19,633 --> 01:17:20,767
- THEY'RE DEAD!

1072
01:17:20,800 --> 01:17:21,767
- SHH!

1073
01:17:21,800 --> 01:17:23,433
YOU NEED TO BE QUIET.

1074
01:17:23,467 --> 01:17:27,367
SHH, SHH, YOU NEED--
YOU NEED TO BE QUIET.

1075
01:17:37,500 --> 01:17:40,067
I WON'T LET YOU HURT HER.

1076
01:17:40,067 --> 01:17:41,300
I WON'T LET YOU.

1077
01:17:41,333 --> 01:17:45,067
- THESE PEOPLE,
THEY DON'T CARE ABOUT YOU.

1078
01:17:45,100 --> 01:17:46,733
THEY'RE ROTTEN.

1079
01:17:46,767 --> 01:17:51,300
EVEN YOUR MOTHER.

1080
01:17:54,900 --> 01:17:59,433
- YOU DID WHAT YOU HAD TO.

1081
01:17:59,467 --> 01:18:01,400
I SEE THAT NOW.

1082
01:18:01,433 --> 01:18:04,467
I UNDERSTAND.

1083
01:18:04,500 --> 01:18:09,100
BUT ALEX IS ALL WE HAVE LEFT.

1084
01:18:10,600 --> 01:18:14,233
SHE'S ONE OF US, DAD.

1085
01:18:14,267 --> 01:18:18,267
SHE'S FAMILY.

1086
01:18:18,300 --> 01:18:21,433
WE CAN--WE CAN START OVER.

1087
01:18:21,467 --> 01:18:24,933
JUST US THREE.

1088
01:18:24,967 --> 01:18:28,767
WE CAN FIX EVERYTHING THAT MOM
RUINED WHEN SHE LEFT.

1089
01:18:28,800 --> 01:18:30,967
- I JUST WANT
WHAT'S BEST FOR YOU.

1090
01:18:31,067 --> 01:18:32,600
YOU'RE MY LITTLE GIRL.

1091
01:18:32,633 --> 01:18:35,200
- I KNOW.

1092
01:18:39,067 --> 01:18:42,967
- I LOVE YOU SO MUCH, SWEETIE.

1093
01:18:43,067 --> 01:18:45,933
SO MUCH.

1094
01:18:45,967 --> 01:18:50,900
- I KNOW.

1095
01:18:50,933 --> 01:18:54,100
WE CAN BE
WHAT WE SHOULD'VE BEEN

1096
01:18:54,133 --> 01:18:57,467
FROM THE BEGINNING.

1097
01:19:01,567 --> 01:19:04,467
- A FAMILY.

1098
01:19:17,800 --> 01:19:19,600
- DAD, NO!

1099
01:19:19,633 --> 01:19:21,633
- [screams]

1100
01:19:21,667 --> 01:19:24,467
- AHH!

1101
01:19:28,867 --> 01:19:29,967
- BRIGG!

1102
01:19:30,067 --> 01:19:31,867
STOP IT!

1103
01:19:31,900 --> 01:19:33,833
BRIGG!

1104
01:19:36,567 --> 01:19:37,600
BRIGG!

1105
01:19:37,633 --> 01:19:38,700
STOP IT!

1106
01:19:38,733 --> 01:19:42,100
PLEASE!

1107
01:19:42,133 --> 01:19:45,133
PLEASE.

1108
01:19:51,633 --> 01:19:54,867
IT'S OKAY.
IT'S OKAY.

1109
01:19:54,900 --> 01:19:57,467
IT'S OKAY.

