1121
01:22:30,967 --> 01:22:33,633
- AND THINGS WITH YOUR
GRANDPARENTS?

1122
01:22:33,667 --> 01:22:36,933
- THEY'RE FINE.

1123
01:22:36,967 --> 01:22:40,767
- I WANNA TALK TO YOU
ABOUT YOUR SISTER.

1124
01:22:40,800 --> 01:22:46,267
