FOR WHAT HAPPENED?

1126
01:22:51,333 --> 01:22:54,833
- NO.

1127
01:22:54,867 --> 01:23:00,833
- * GET BACK TOGETHER

1128
01:23:00,867 --> 01:23:02,833
